s to the Company’s valuation allowances may be necessary.", "bbox": [104.2, 1316.6, 853.8, 1339.7]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2014, the Company had approximately $365.0 million state net operating loss carry-forwards expiring", "bbox": [154.2, 1360.4, 1159.2, 1383.5]}, {"text": "in 2031. At December 31, 2014 the Company also had Wisconsin research and development credit carryforwards of $13.7", "bbox": [104.2, 1385.4, 1126.4, 1408.5]}, {"text": "million expiring in 2028. The Company had a deferred tax asset of $27.8 million as of December 31, 2014 for the benefit of", "bbox": [104.2, 1410.4, 1141.7, 1433.5]}, {"text": "these losses and credits. A valuation allowance of $4.8 million has been established against the deferred tax asset.", "bbox": [104.2, 1435.4, 1049.6, 1458.5]}, {"text": "The Company has foreign net operating losses (NOL) totaling $14.2 million as of December 31, 2014. It has a valuation", "bbox": [154.2, 1479.1, 1161.5, 1502.2]}, {"text": "allowance of $20.7 million against the NOLs as well as other associated deferred tax assets.", "bbox": [104.2, 1504.1, 869.0, 1527.2]}]}